A031876.name: a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} floor(k^(1/3)).
formula: a(0) = 0, a(1) = 1, a(n) = 2*a(n-1) - a(n-2) if n not a perfect cube, else a(n) = 2*a(n-1) - a(n-2) + 1 if n is a perfect cube.
